  "contenu": [
    {
      "id": "b1d53f7d-561c-411b-a1ba-87018ad1bea0",
      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soit $E$ un espace vectoriel euclidien orienté de dimension 3, $\\vec u \\in E$ unitaire,\n$\\alpha \\in \\R$ et $f$ la rotation autour de $\\vec u$ d'angle de mesure $\\alpha$.",
        "html": "<p>Soit <span class=\"math inline\">\\(E\\)</span> un espace vectoriel euclidien orienté de dimension 3, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\vec u \\in E\\)</span> unitaire, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\alpha \\in \\R\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span> la rotation autour de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\vec u\\)</span> d’angle de mesure <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\alpha\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "a3ad0011-3b94-413e-b87b-6303419fc70c",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Exprimer $f(\\vec x)$ en fonction de $\\vec u$, $\\vec x$ et $\\alpha$.",
        "html": "<p>Exprimer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f(\\vec x)\\)</span> en fonction de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\vec u\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\vec x\\)</span> et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\alpha\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "0fd80ed8-a606-41cb-9162-4a8e79c82b7e",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$f(\\vec x) = (\\vec x|\\vec u)\\vec u\n                        + \\cos\\alpha(\\vec u\\wedge\\vec x)\\wedge\\vec u\n                        + \\sin\\alpha(\\vec u\\wedge\\vec x)$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(f(\\vec x) = (\\vec x|\\vec u)\\vec u\n                        + \\cos\\alpha(\\vec u\\wedge\\vec x)\\wedge\\vec u\n                        + \\sin\\alpha(\\vec u\\wedge\\vec x)\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "7c0c4ab6-520f-4722-a333-5f46a3dbb109",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "On donne les coordonnées de $\\vec u$ dans une base orthonormée : $a,b,c$.\n    Calculer la matrice de $f$ dans cette base.",
        "html": "<p>On donne les coordonnées de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\vec u\\)</span> dans une base orthonormée : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(a,b,c\\)</span>. Calculer la matrice de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(f\\)</span> dans cette base.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "f6649690-71d9-4224-9bed-573eb0ecccad",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$M = (\\cos\\alpha)I\n                + (1-\\cos\\alpha)\\begin{pmatrix}a^2 &ab &ac \\cr\n                                         ab &b^2 &bc \\cr\n                                         ac &bc &c^2 \\cr \\end{pmatrix}\n                + \\sin\\alpha\\begin{pmatrix}0  &-c &b \\cr\n                                     c  &0  &-a \\cr\n                                     -b &a  &0 \\cr\\end{pmatrix}$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(M = (\\cos\\alpha)I\n                + (1-\\cos\\alpha)\\begin{pmatrix}a^2 &amp;ab &amp;ac \\cr\n                                         ab &amp;b^2 &amp;bc \\cr\n                                         ac &amp;bc &amp;c^2 \\cr \\end{pmatrix}\n                + \\sin\\alpha\\begin{pmatrix}0  &amp;-c &amp;b \\cr\n                                     c  &amp;0  &amp;-a \\cr\n                                     -b &amp;a  &amp;0 \\cr\\end{pmatrix}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
